# Axentra v1.2.0 Changelog
Released: 14-03-2026

---

## :toolbox: Virtual Block Commands
- Added /anvil - opens an anvil without a physical block
- Added /workbench - opens a crafting table without a physical block (aliases: /wb, /craft, /craftingtable)
- Added /cartography - opens a cartography table without a physical block (aliases: /carto, /cartographytable)
- Added /grindstone - opens a grindstone without a physical block (aliases: /grind)
- Added /loom - opens a loom without a physical block
- Added /smithingtable - opens a smithing table without a physical block (aliases: /smithing, /smith)
- Added /stonecutter - opens a stonecutter without a physical block (aliases: /stone)
- Added /enderchest - opens your ender chest from anywhere (aliases: /ec, /echest)

## :zap: Utility Commands
- Added /hat - places the item in your hand on your head as a helmet
- Added /ping [player] - checks your ping or another player's ping in milliseconds
- Added /suicide - instantly kills yourself
- Added /clearwarns <player> - clears all warnings for a player

## :clock: Time Commands
- Added /time <set|add> <day|noon|night|midnight|ticks> - sets or adds to the world time
- Added shortcuts: /day, /noon, /night, /midnight

## :cloud_rain: Weather Commands
- Added /weather <clear|rain|storm> - sets the weather in the world
- Added shortcuts: /sun, /sky, /rain, /storm

## :information_source: Axentra Command
- /axentra information now shows the support Discord link

