# Axentra v1.1.0 Changelog
Released: 09-03-2026

---

## :mute: Mute System
- Added /mute <player> [reason] - mutes a player from the chat
- Added /unmute <player> - unmutes a player
- Mute state is stored in SQLite database
- Supports announce-mute and announce-unmute toggles in config.yml

## :warning: Warn System
- Added /warn <player> [reason] - warns a player with a reason
- Added /warns [player] - shows all warnings for a player
- Warn count is tracked and shown to the player on each warn
- Supports announce-warn toggle in config.yml
- Added warn-punishments system in config.yml:
  - Automatically applies a punishment at a set warn count
  - Supported actions: kick, mute, tempban, ban
  - Tempban action supports custom duration (e.g. 1d, 12h)

## :heart: Heal & Feed Commands
- Added /heal [player] - restores health, food and saturation
- Added /feed [player] - restores food level and saturation
- Both support self and others with separate permissions
- Axentra.heal / Axentra.heal.others
- Axentra.feed / Axentra.feed.others

## :hammer: IP Ban System
- Added /banip <player|ip> [reason] - bans an IP address permanently
- Added /unbanip <ip> - unbans an IP address
- Added /tempbanip <player|ip> <duration> [reason] - temporarily bans an IP
- Accepts both player names (resolves their IP automatically) and raw IPs
- Kicks all online players matching the banned IP on ban
- Supports announce-banip toggle in config.yml

## :stopwatch: Temp Ban System
- Added /tempban <player> <duration> [reason] - temporarily bans a player
- Duration format: combinations of d, h, m, s (e.g. 1d12h, 30m, 7d)
- Tab complete suggestions: 1h, 1d, 7d, 30d
- Expiry stored in SQLite database
- Uses announce-ban toggle from config.yml

## :lock: New Permissions
- Axentra.mute
- Axentra.unmute
- Axentra.warn
- Axentra.warns
- Axentra.heal / Axentra.heal.others
- Axentra.feed / Axentra.feed.others
- Axentra.banip
- Axentra.unbanip
- Axentra.tempban
- Axentra.tempbanip